<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>사진 앨범</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>📸 나의 추억 앨범</h2>
        <p>QR 코드를 통해 공유된 사진입니다.</p>

        <div class="album-gallery">
            <% images.forEach(image => { %>
                <img src="<%= image %>" alt="앨범 사진" class="album-image">
            <% }); %>
        </div>

        <br>
        <a href="/" class="custom-file-upload">🏠 다시 업로드</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
